--- 
title: Design, User Experience and Front End Development portfolio - Cathy Dutton 
description: A collection of my work from employers including Defra, Barclays, EE, The Hut Group and AO.com 
layout: layouts/base.njk 
permalink: /projects/ 
pageName: Projects 
---



<header id="js-skip-link-target" class="page-header clear">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <h1>
     Projects
    </h1>
    <p class="page-intro">Design and Front End Development work</p>
    {% include "socialMedia.njk" %}
  </div>
</header>

<div class="wrapper">

  <p class="highlight-text">
    Over the years I have had the pleasure of working for some amazing companies and brands on a range of digital projects. Below are just a few examples of my design and development work. 
  </p>

  <section class="cards">
    {% for post in collections.projects %}
      <article class="card js-content-group" data-url="{{ post.url }}" data-title="{{post.data.title}}">
        <div class="image-ratio">
          <img data-src="{{ post.data.image }}" class="lazyload" alt="Cover image for {{ post.data.title }}">
        </div>
        <h3 class="card__title">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            <span class="visually-hidden">Project title</span>
            {{ post.data.title }}
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p class="card__date">
          <span class="visually-hidden">Project date</span>
          <time datetime="{{ post.data.date }}">{{ post.data.date | dateDisplayProject }}</time>
        </p>
        {% if post.data.projectTags %}
          <p class="card__tags">Tagged in:
            {% for projectTag in post.data.projectTags %}
              <a href="/projects/tags/{{ projectTag | lower | replace(" ", "-") }}" class="anchor">{{ projectTag }}</a>
              {% if not loop.last %},
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </p>
        {% endif %}
      </article>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </section>

</div>
